quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  29,26,"Iumen it Luî. Inna: \"nek, d iminig ar Mass iw. Ih, Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  29,27,"N$at it s Isêaq akked Yaâqub. I tarwas, Nefka lambiyya, Tazmamt. Nefka yas taqviât is, di ddunit; u neppa, di laxeôt, war ccekk, seg iâaôviyen"
  29,28,"Luî, mi inna i ugdud is: \"ih, aql akwen la txedmem lâaô, ur ixdim yiwen, zik, deg imavalen"
  29,29,"La teppeddum, ih, ar irgazen, tgezzmem abrid, txeddmem ayen icemten, deg igrawen nnwen\". Tiririt n ugdud is, siwa mi nnan: \"awi a$ d aâaqeb n Öebbi, ma telliv seg wid issawalen tidep"
  29,30,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Efk iyi afus, mgal agdud ifessaden"
  29,31,"Mi d usan imceggâen nne£, ar Ibôahim, s ubecceô, nnan as: \"ih, a Nesqucc imezda$ n temdint agi. Imezda$ is, s tidep, d imednas"
  29,32,"Inna d: \"ni$ degs Luî\". Nnan as: \"Nekwni, Neéôa sennig akw, i illan degs. A t Naâteq, neppa akked twacult is, siwa tameîîut is, ara yilin seg wid igwran"
  29,33,"Mi usan imceggâen nne£, ar Luî, i$wbel ilmend nnsen, ur izmir a ten ifukk. Nnan as: \"ur ppagwad, ur $webbel. Nekwni a k Naâteq, keçç d twacult ik, siwa tameîîut ik, ara yilin seg wid igwran"
  29,34,"Ih, nekwni a d Nesse$li ssxev seg igenni, $ef imezda$ n temdint agi, ilmend n lâaô nnsen"
  29,35,"Ni$ Neooa d segs, assekni iberrzen, i ugdud ipmeyyizen"
  29,36,"Ar Madian, gmat sen Cuâayeb. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi, gganit ass aneggaru, ur oouôut di tmurt d ifessaden"
  29,37,"Nekôen t. Tewwet iten zzenzla. Gwran d, d loeppat, deg ixxamen nnsen"
  29,38,"Âad akked Tamud - ni$ iban awen d seg ixxamen nnsen -, icebbeê asen Cciîan igiten nnsen. Issuffe$ iten seg ubrid, nitni pfeôôioen"
  29,39,"Qaôun, Ferâun, Haman, ni$ iusa ten id Musa, s ubeggen. Sme$wôen iman nnsen, di tmurt, ur rbiêen"
  29,40,"Yal wa, Newwet it $ef ubekkav is. Llan wid iwumi Nuzen tabucivant. Llan wid i iwwet usu$u. Llan wid i Nger seddaw wakal. Llan wid i Ne$meq. Maççi d Öebbi iten idensen, d nitni i idensen iman nnsen"
  29,41,"Wid iteddun d imawlan, war Öebbi, cban rtila. Tebna tissist. Ihi, axxam ahcican mavi, d tissist n rtila, lemmer ssinen"
  29,42,"Ih, Öebbi Iéôa akw ayen u$uô naâôen, war Neppa. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  29,43,"Imedyaten agi, Neppawi ten id, i l$aci. Siwa imusnawen ara ten ifehmen"
  29,44,"Ixleq Öebbi tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Ih, deg waya, assekni i lmumnin"
  29,45,"Mel ayen i k id ippuweêêan si Tezmamt. Bedd i téallit. Ih, taéallit teppekkes lâaô, tuccva. War ccek, iugar ip usmekti n Öebbi. Öebbi Iéôa acu tûenâam"